      "headline": "Antonio Bicchi: over 41 years, 210 papers, 11,570 total cites, h=51, 4 blockbusters (500+ cites).",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Started in 1985 with \"Tendon actuated exploratory finger with polymeric, skin-like tactile sensor\". First 500+ cite paper came 10 years in: \"On the Closure Properties of Robotic Grasping\" (1995, 531 cites). 1000+ cite paper: \"Robotic Grasping and Contact: A Review\" (2000, 1,056 cites).",
