        "Authors per paper: early 2.7 → late 5.7 (team growth).",
        "Peak paper \"Robotic Grasping and Contact: A Review\" (2000, 1,056 cites) — fell in mid career.",
        "58 likely students — top: Giorgio Grioli(2008~, we last-author on 16), Manuel G. Catalano(2009~, we last-author on 15), Marco Gabiccini(2010~, we last-author on 14)."
